{"tid":2029484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"洗版網絡trend可唔可行？","createTime":"2020-05-22T09:00:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T10:45:41.000Z","uid":359022,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f8bd4fa9e39a8cd5b64347b782cb3c35d53ebb67","tid":2029484,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:00:43.000Z","msg":"google忽然del曬黃色相關關鍵詞之後跪低<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以食住個勢，趁國安法未到，洗版香港獨立唯一出路，變成網絡trend。就好似#五大訴求缺一不可，#5DN1L，屎近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美眾議員提法案　授權特朗普承認香港屬獨立國家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2029007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2029007</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n不論係google、twitter定ig，希望見到打 香港，會出現：<br />\n<br />\n獨立，唯一出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話比全世界聽，香港人嘅熱度同決心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係p牌仔小弟第一個post，ac今日先註冊到。終於搞一大輪拎番個email，dig起心肝唔做cd-rom。點解5毛可以咁輕而易舉開到ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"887cda2c756b4ea03f3ca439d7deb016839a5046","tid":2029484,"uid":125502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NkRzx1A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNkRzx1A.gif&h=65e3b426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">見到連鄺俊宇自己都保唔住，你仲相信「溫柔是最大的勇武嗎？」</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取消功能組別 五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全民習武 唯一出路</span></strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"9aa2311c575c211c28bb29cc9aff606016f9a6cf","tid":2029484,"uid":280056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:05:04.000Z","ms